"""
videonorma-daemon — watches directories for new videos and offers normalization.
https://github.com/prostopasta/videonorma

Requires: python3-watchdog  gir1.2-ayatanaappindicator3-0.1 (Ubuntu/Debian)
          python3-watchdog  libayatana-appindicator-gtk3    (Fedora/Arch)
"""

